  "original_title": "Four suspects further remanded till Aug. 10",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Four suspects further remanded till Aug. 10",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Four suspects arrested over the incident of setting fire to President Ranil Wickremesinghe's private residence in Colombo were ordered to be further remanded till August 10 by Colombo Fort Magistrate's Court.",
        "These four suspects were today produced before an identification parade and they were ordered to be further remanded after being produced before Colombo Fort Magistrate Thilina Gamage.",
        "Meanwhile, the CID has named another person who was allegedly involved in the incident as the fifth suspect in the case. The CID had informed the court that an individual named Evan Perera wanted for questioning over the incident has already been fled the country and the airport authorities have been informed in this regard. (Lakmal Sooriyagoda)"
      ],
